about.summary: Contains miscellaneous functions useful in biostatistics, mostly univariate and multivariate testing procedures with a special emphasis on permutation tests. Many functions intend to simplify user's life by shortening existing procedures or by implementing plotting functions that can be used with as many methods from different packages as possible.

name: r-rvaidememoire
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9-75" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rvaidememoire
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RVAideMemoire_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RVAideMemoire/RVAideMemoire_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 374c2cc2af27089990cd33f8b9bd5b20cb7c83d7c3afad4e0c60307a3ced8f93

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-factominer
    - r-mass
    - r-ade4 >=1.7_8
    - r-boot
    - r-car
    - r-cramer
    - r-lme4 >=1.0_4
    - r-mixomics
    - r-nnet
    - r-pls
    - r-pspearman
    - r-vegan >=2.4_3
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-factominer
    - r-mass
    - r-ade4 >=1.7_8
    - r-boot
    - r-car
    - r-cramer
    - r-lme4 >=1.0_4
    - r-mixomics
    - r-nnet
    - r-pls
    - r-pspearman
    - r-vegan >=2.4_3

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RVAideMemoire')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RVAideMemoire')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=RVAideMemoire
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Contains miscellaneous functions useful in biostatistics, mostly univariate and multivariate testing procedures with a special emphasis on permutation
    tests. Many functions intend to simplify user's life by shortening existing procedures or by implementing plotting functions that can be used with as many methods
    from different packages as possible.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
